languages.text: Солдаты погибли в ожесточенной перестрелке, но кто в кого стрелял — не ясно.

traits.locale_text: Солдаты погибли в ожесточенной перестрелке, но кто в кого стрелял — не ясно.

languages.text: These soldiers died in a brutal exchange of fire, but it is unclear who was shooting at whom.

languages.text: 这些士兵在激烈的交火中阵亡，但并不清楚当时是谁在朝谁开枪。
languages.original_text: These soldiers died in a brutal exchange of fire, but it is unclear who was shooting at whom.

traits.locale_text: 这些士兵在激烈的交火中阵亡，但并不清楚当时是谁在朝谁开枪。

languages.text: Estos soldados murieron durante un brutal tiroteo, pero no queda claro quién disparaba a quién.
languages.original_text: These soldiers died in a brutal exchange of fire, but it is unclear who was shooting at whom.

traits.locale_text: Estos soldados murieron durante un brutal tiroteo, pero no queda claro quién disparaba a quién.

languages.text: この兵士たちは激しい銃撃戦のすえに死亡したようだが、誰が誰に向けて撃っていたのかは不明だ。
languages.original_text: These soldiers died in a brutal exchange of fire, but it is unclear who was shooting at whom.

traits.locale_text: この兵士たちは激しい銃撃戦のすえに死亡したようだが、誰が誰に向けて撃っていたのかは不明だ。

languages.text: Diese Soldaten sind bei einem brutalen Feuergefecht gestorben, aber es ist unklar, wer auf wen geschossen hat.
languages.original_text: These soldiers died in a brutal exchange of fire, but it is unclear who was shooting at whom.

traits.locale_text: Diese Soldaten sind bei einem brutalen Feuergefecht gestorben, aber es ist unklar, wer auf wen geschossen hat.

languages.text: Ces soldats sont morts des suites d'une fusillade sauvage, mais impossible de dire qui tirait sur qui.
languages.original_text: These soldiers died in a brutal exchange of fire, but it is unclear who was shooting at whom.

traits.locale_text: Ces soldats sont morts des suites d'une fusillade sauvage, mais impossible de dire qui tirait sur qui.

languages.text: Bu askerler şiddetli bir çatışma sonucunda ölmüşler. Kimin kime ateş ettiği ise belli değil.

traits.locale_text: Bu askerler şiddetli bir çatışma sonucunda ölmüşler ama kim kime ateş ediyormuş belli değil.
